# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# type:
#   feat     ✨ A new feature
#   fix      🐛 A bug fix
#   docs     📚 Documentation changes
#   style    🎨 Code style (no functional change)
#   refactor 🔨 Refactor (neither feature nor fix)
#   perf     ⚡ Performance improvement
#   test     🧪 Add or update tests
#   build    📦 Build system or dependencies
#   ci       🔧 CI configuration
#   chore    🔩 Other changes
#   revert   ◀️  Revert a previous commit
#
# scope (optional):
#   core     ipatool-core library
#   cli      ipatool-cli binary
#   deps     dependency updates
#
# subject: imperative mood, lowercase, no trailing period
#
# body (optional): explain the motivation and approach
#
# footer (optional):
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   Closes #<issue>
#   Refs #<issue>
#
# Examples:
#   feat(core): add App Store search API support
#   fix(cli): handle download timeout gracefully
#   docs: update README with installation instructions
#   refactor(core): extract HTTP client into separate module
